      "MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|5856,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|253182,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|274783,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|575068,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|311036",
